channel.title: Tried to run my new client
channel.description:
..and this came up:
Exception in thread "main" java.lang.NoClassDefFoundError: Jframe Caused by:java.lang.ClassNotFoundException: Jframe at java.net.URLClassLoader$1.run(URLClassLoader.java:202) at java.security.AccessController.doPrivileged(Native Method) at java.net.URLClassLoader.loadClass(ClassLoader.java:190) at java.lang.ClassLoader.loadClass(ClassLoader.java:307) at sun.misc.Launcher$AppClassLoader.loadClass(Launcher.java:301) at java.lang.ClassLoader.loadclass(ClassLoader.java:248) Could not find the main class: Jframe. Program will exit. Press any key to continue . . .
I'm guessing i need a main class "Jframe"? Anybody else know what to do?
i'm trying to get this client running, i would really appreciate any help anyone could offer my msn -- drs023@hotmail.com
